						               													<description>An escalating roll and move racing game where players strategically purchase and use upgrades and items in an effort to be the first to finish 10 laps.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player begins with $4000 and some free items of their choice. Players roll dice and move their cars around the board, then interact with the spaces they land on. Players can accumulate items purchased from shops which allow them to move further on each turn, use boosters, sabotage opponents, take shortcuts, earn extra money, and more. Players interact with other spaces they land on to move further, take a shortcut, earn extra money, or to gain or lose a turn. Players earn more money upon completion of each lap.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Different items the players purchase offer different strategies. Players can focus on upgrading speed, purchasing items that give options, taking shortcuts, or investing in money gaining items early so they can buy everything and make a blazing comeback. The first player to finish the 10th lap wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
